Para 
\begin_inset Formula $a,b\in\mathbb{K}$
\end_inset

 y 
\begin_inset Formula $x,y,z\in H$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\langle x,ay+bz\rangle=\overline{a}\langle x,y\rangle+\overline{b}\langle x,z\rangle$
\end_inset

.
